data.description:
Great home in a quiet neighborhood. Recently remodeled and updated. New windows, flooring, carpet, updated light fixtures, new paint, brand new appliances, renovated kitchen, bathroom and new furnace. Conveniently located, near schools, shopping, parks, restaurants and bus stops!
On the main floor, you'll find 1 bedroom, a full bathroom, spacious kitchen, dining and living room (open floor plan).Upstairs you will find two spacious bedrooms and a walk-in closet. Enclosed front porch, garage and a fenced in backyard, perfect for family gatherings. This property sits on a double lot. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!  Call for your private showing today!
